<h3 id="assignment">Assignment</h3>

<p>Spend 20 minutes working on the first challenge in the exercise. Implement the solution twice, using 2 of the following looping tools:</p>

<ul>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">each</code></li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">for</code> loop</li>
  <li><code class="highlighter-rouge">while</code> loop</li>
</ul>

<p>Then spend 5 - 10 minutes recapping and sharing solutions for that exercise</p>

<p>Next spend 30 minutes working on the second challenge. Again, implement it twice using 2 of the available looping techniques.</p>
